data.description: Back on the market! No fault of property. Seller very motivated to sell quick! Take advantage of this spacious 4 bedroom 2 full baths on a 1 story 2,018 sq.ft. no need to go up and down stairs. Laundry area inside house. Master bedroom is spacious with dual sinks, shower stall is separate from tub. Also, has a walk in closet. Kitchen has room for eat in kitchen table. Family room /kitchen combo.  Walking distance to park. Easy access to HWY 101. Storage shed convey with sale.
